{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"30":"Chapters on Drinks"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3376,"arabicnumber":3376,"text":"It was narrated from Abu Darda’ that the Prophet (ﷺ) said:“No one who is addicted to wine will enter Paradise.”","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan Or Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":30,"hadith":6}}]}